{
  "stem": "18665.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we were brought into Hongkew, where this Kinchow Road Camp was and other camps were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was the cheapest neighborhood in the city to, to settle down and find a room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 18.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my first job was with a-- as a secretary, private secretary, to a Eurasian man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his name was T.R.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Crank.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I worked for him for six months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But once he found out that I learned to speak Chinese from one of the employees, he fired me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He didn't like that I learned the language so I wouldn't find out what his business was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after that, I got a job as a broker for several firms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the last one, before the war broke out, was with a Dutch firm called Sino-Java Import and Export Firm.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was hired on a-- first, on a trial basis.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But even that never finished because November 10th, as it was for us, the-- December, December 8th-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "December 8th, Pearl Harbor broke out, and that was the end of that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they, they let me go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that area.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, it was still not considered a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just a, a poor district of Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We always-- I've always worked in different capacities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- my father also had-- started an import business in fur, which could have been very successful if it wasn't for Pearl Harbor.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that shut everything off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- in, I believe, in mid '43, the Japanese had a proclamation-- actually, it came out of '42-- that by a certain date, all status refugees had to move into the district, or ghetto, as we now call it.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was Hongkew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they put barbed wire around it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
